Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆諸島已進入風速25m/s的暴風雨區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到2點為止的 最大瞬間風速為36.1m/s
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近海域發生大浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣象廳預測今日關東地區也將進入暴風雨區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雨的同時請大家注意山泥傾瀉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括航空在內的各項交通預計也將受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於颱風前進路線上的關東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在繼續保持嚴密的戒備狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直擊的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京都內各地區…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鷺月子的手提包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從犯罪現場拿走的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆是不可能襲擊鷺月子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 能否告訴我們一點當時的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時希望你能協助我們指認嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們到署裏走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見我孫女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你孫女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從她父母的公司破產後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就家不成家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回家卻無家可歸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子肯定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被寄養在嬸嬸家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說不久就離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你賠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帶那種東西回學校的你不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家裏不給你買遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才告的密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師完了 又是爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妙子長大了 要當爸爸的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的新娘是媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嘛 妙子也要當嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好相似的父女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裏都是「爸爸」、「爸爸」的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想聽的不是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當晚 你看到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到什麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無家可歸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時在現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拿著這個手提包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了罪行的每個細節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都只有那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家怎麼可能有那種閒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人說馬上就要辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那孩子也差不多到那年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 至少得有自己的書房呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 也只有這麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不期望太高就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我出生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要保持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有臉打來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊 我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那裏不是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種家 沒了更好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉 得回請你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的那件案子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來組長的想法是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣的話 狐塚到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螳螂捕蟬 黃雀在後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿犯罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 回到署裏再嚴加審問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從別處入手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再被弄得一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別處是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來和媽媽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 你察覺背後有人 一轉頭就被襲擊了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒看清兇徒的樣子 不過身高…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球棒少年」抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在定案之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再確認一下作案時的詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你配合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 關於那個兇徒的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去澀谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 不是已經搬完家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不給面子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一個重要的日子 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很吃驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒見到兇徒以外的其他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該把真相說出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起如此大的騷動 已經進退兩難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽川津說 你在案發的那段期間裏似乎很苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公司被孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個作品的完成期限也逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連草稿都沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說簡單些 就是被逼得想逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被道路魔襲擊的話 就會變得非常輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它當時也在場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你遇襲的停車場排水道裏找到了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經得到當晚案件目擊者的證供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎 在我小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要全部毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毀掉你的全部幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很苦惱 不知該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 你走在回家的夜路上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老婆婆並非消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆的帳篷就在停車場附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位老婆婆說她看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想從壓迫感中逃脫出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘掉一切的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在停車場找到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己打傷了自己的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 喂 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 回答我 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房子 我的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 妙子 妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺小姐 怎麼了 鷺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 趕快抬到候審室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給關東地區造成巨大損失的9號颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其強度已經急速減退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜已經進入太平洋 演變為熱帶低氣壓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣象廳今早已解除東京都內的所有警報信號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}各部分交通也已經恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫柴崎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到通知說祖母她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小綠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙子 真被你說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「家」沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從關東科學的縫隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,側耳傾聽則成賢者之言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著狐貍的足跡徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片悲怨的草地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 名偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.72,0:24:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
